Avenir Telecom Logo
Avenir Telecom is a telecommunication products' distributor and related services' provider. It is one of the leading companies in the European market. The major shareholder is the holding company OXO. The Company has worldwide operations. They consist in the distribution and sale of a wide variety of communication products, especially mobile phones, activation of service, accessories, answering and fax machines, phone cases, phone chargers, phone soxs, plastic shelves, 3D phone stickers for mobiles and laptops, earkits, hands-free kits, portable headsets, and USB Bluetooth dongles under the OXO name.
You can download theAvenir Telecomlogo on full-version of the page.
